
~~Variables:
--Static types and Dynamic typed.
--Are use to stored the data (any kind of data)
--1) Case-Sensitive
--2) start with letters,_(under-score), $(dollar-sign)
--3) can't start with numbers
--4) Reserved words(keywords) not allowed
--5) Allow letters, _(under-score), $(dollar-sign), numbers


1)Reassigning variables is possible by var
2)Reassigning with let also accepted
3)Reassigning with const not accepted


--Redeclaring with var is accepted
--Redeclaring with let is not accepted
--Redeclaring with const is not accepted


Block scope:
--Variables declared with var doesn't have a block scope
--declared with let has a block scope

